Project: ReviewSense - Customer Review Intelligence Platform
Hackathon: Hack Malenadu '26
Stack: React+Vite+TailwindCSS / Node.js+Express+MongoDB / Python FastAPI
Models: cardiffnlp sentiment, yangheng ABSA, Helsinki-NLP translation
Pattern: Same as MedShield project structure
Rules:
- All API responses: { success: bool, data: {}, message: str }
- All async functions: try/catch with proper error handling
- TailwindCSS only, no inline styles
- lucide-react for all icons
- Add console.log at every major processing step







.\venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
uvicorn main:app --reload --port 8000